 om NetApp. In the second part of the presentation we will discuss the conf
 iguration details necessary in Cinder (and OpenStack) to allow live migrat
 ion of instances to work with block storage attached.  
LOCATION:Austin Convention Center - Level 4 - MR 12 A/B 
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
